{"type":null,"faqId":43858,"title":"为何B2偶尔跟华为手机会频繁自动断连？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>出现此问题时，请用户检查手机wifi是否打开，一般此问题是蓝牙与wifi同时打开的情况下会概率出现，由于蓝牙、wifi共用天线，处于同频段，wifi可能会对蓝牙造成干扰。出现此问题</span><span class=\"s1\">将wifi开关重置后即可恢复。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9359","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399710000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":8,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B,连接,断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}